OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774534301
OL,3,CTwo Hampshire councils to be abolished
OL,4,Cin major democracy shake-up
OL,6,FThe cities of Southampton and
OL,7,FPortsmouth are to lose their own
OL,8,Fdedicated city councils in the biggest
OL,9,Fshake-up of local democracy in
OL,10,FHampshire since the 1970s.
OL,12,FThe government has announced that the
OL,13,Ftwo cities' local authorities will be
OL,14,Fmerged with neighbouring district and
OL,15,Fborough councils.
OL,17,FAcross Hampshire and the Isle of
OL,18,FWight, 15 local authorities will be
OL,19,Fscrapped and replaced with five new
OL,20,Funitary authorities.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
