FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774534301
OL,3,CTwo Hampshire councils to be abolished
OL,4,Cin major democracy shake-up
OL,6,FThese so-called 'mega councils' will
OL,7,Fbe responsible for everything from
OL,8,Frubbish collections to adult social
OL,9,Fcare and bring to an end two-tier
OL,10,Flocal government, with separate county
OL,11,Fand district authorities.
OL,13,FPortsmouth City Council will be merged
OL,14,Fwith Fareham, Gosport, Havant, and
OL,15,Fparts of East Hampshire and
OL,16,FWinchester. The new authority will be
OL,17,Fknown as South East Hampshire Council.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
