PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774534301
OL,3,CTwo Hampshire councils to be abolished
OL,4,Cin major democracy shake-up
OL,6,FSouthampton City Council will be
OL,7,Freplaced by a new South West Hampshire
OL,8,FCouncil, encompassing Eastleigh and
OL,9,Fparts of the current New Forest and
OL,10,FTest Valley council areas.
OL,12,FThe two south coast cities have had
OL,13,Findividual councils since 1836.
OL,14,FPortsmouth gained city status in 1926,
OL,15,Fwith Southampton following suit in
OL,16,F1964.
OL,18,FNorth Hampshire Council will be formed
OL,19,Ffrom the current councils of
OL,20,FBasingstoke and Deane, Hart and
OL,21,FRushmoor.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
