FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774534301
OL,3,CTwo Hampshire councils to be abolished
OL,4,Cin major democracy shake-up
OL,6,FA Mid Hampshire Council will be
OL,7,Fcreated from parts of East Hampshire,
OL,8,FNew Forest, Test Valley and Winchester.
OL,10,FThe Isle of Wight will maintain its
OL,11,Fown separate local authority.
OL,13,FThe decision has been made by the
OL,14,FCommunities Secretary Steve Reed and
OL,15,Fis subject to parliamentary approval.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
