PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774534301
OL,3,CTwo Hampshire councils to be abolished
OL,4,Cin major democracy shake-up
OL,6,FMr Reed said in a statement:
OL,7,F"Reorganisation presents a once-in-a-
OL,8,Fgeneration chance to make sure our
OL,9,Fcouncils match the modern realities of
OL,10,Four places, making sure outdated
OL,11,Fboundaries are not constraining
OL,12,Fgrowth, particularly in our towns and
OL,13,Fcities."
OL,15,FA decision on reorganising councils
OL,16,Facross Sussex has been delayed.
OL,18,FSteve Reed said that after "carefully
OL,19,Fconsidering the four proposals
OL,20,Freceived " he had "not yet made a
OL,21,Fdecision".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
