PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774534301
OL,3,CTwo Hampshire councils to be abolished
OL,4,Cin major democracy shake-up
OL,6,FThe Communitieis Secretary said he had
OL,7,F"concerns regarding all four of the
OL,8,Fproposals" and was "considering
OL,9,Fmodifications" to them.
OL,11,FElections to the new unitary councils
OL,12,Fin Hampshire are scheduled to take
OL,13,Fplace in May 2027, ahead of them
OL,14,Ftaking over the delivery of services
OL,15,Fin April 2028.
