PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774534301
OL,3,CTwo Hampshire councils to be abolished
OL,4,Cin major democracy shake-up
OL,6,FNatalie Brahma-Pearl, Chief Executive
OL,7,Fof Portsmouth City Council said: "The
OL,8,Fgovernment has announced its decision
OL,9,Fon Local Government Reorganisation,
OL,10,Fwhich will see Portsmouth City Council
OL,11,Fbecome part of a larger unitary
OL,12,Fauthority also covering the areas of
OL,13,FGosport, Fareham and Havant, and
OL,14,Finclude Newlands, Horndean, Clanfield
OL,15,Fand Rowlands Castle.
OL,17,F"We will be working to ensure the best
OL,18,Fpossible outcome for Portsmouth
OL,19,Fresidents and businesses, while
OL,20,Fcontinuing to deliver the vital
OL,21,Fservices our communities rely on."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
