PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774534301
OL,3,CTwo Hampshire councils to be abolished
OL,4,Cin major democracy shake-up
OL,6,FCouncillor Alex Winning, Leader of
OL,7,FSouthampton City Council, said: "This
OL,8,Fis the right decision for our area.
OL,10,F"Bringing together Southampton,
OL,11,FEastleigh, the Waterside and lower
OL,12,FTest Valley creates a council that
OL,13,Freflects the areas people already
OL,14,Ftravel, work and build their lives in.
OL,16,F"It unites our port, airport and
OL,17,Fmaritime industries, strengthens
OL,18,Fstrategic planning, and ensures a
OL,19,Fbalanced, diverse and sustainable
OL,20,Fpopulation across the new authority.
OL,26,@oD@aOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
