CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774534301
OL,3,CTwo Hampshire councils to be abolished
OL,4,Cin major democracy shake-up
OL,6,F"Now that the Government has made its
OL,7,Fdecision, it's right that we come
OL,8,Ftogether and seize this opportunity to
OL,9,Fbuild a new council that delivers
OL,10,Fexcellent services and improves the
OL,11,Flives of local people."
